projectGridLines.title: Title: Software Developers
projectGridLines.description:
Title: Software Developers


Description: Seeking a curious mind to join our team of passionate developers.

Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design, develop, and implement scalable

software solutions. Understand the process from different stakeholders across

multiple teams.

Skill sets: Basic knowledge of Backend and Frontend Frameworks. Solve 100+

problems in Competitive Programming.

Traits expectation: High Intent and Curious Mind. Strong problem-solving skills and

attention to detail. Eagerness to learn and adapt.

Expected learning: Gain proficiency in programming languages including Ruby,

JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and SQL. Experiment with Cloud solutions and

technologies. Familiarise yourself with frameworks such as Ruby on Rails (ROR),

React, React Native, Express, and Liquid.

Specific courses required for project
